[section#stmt.break
    [:en] The [`break] statement
]

[%  [:en] statement[![`break]]
    [:zh_CN] ]

[para]
[:en]
The [`break] statement shall occur only in an
[%[~iteration-statement]] [%statement[![`switch]]]
[~iteration-statement] or a [`switch] statement and causes termination of the
smallest enclosing [~iteration-statement] or [`switch] statement; control passes
to the statement following the terminated statement, if any.
